headline: Starbucks: One Of My Hedges Going Into 2025
summary: Starbucks' premium valuation is harder to justify amid declining performance. Find out why SBUX stock may face more downside, with hedging offering potential gains.

headline: Three Reasons to Avoid SBUX and One Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Starbucks has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 23.1%. The stock now trades at $92.68, marking a 27.8% gain. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
